Dialogs.Dialog: Since we're here, let's take some pictures here.
Rinko
Here？ Great, let's take a shot.
Why don't we take a photo, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
All right. What pose would you like this time？
Why don't we take a photo, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
...here？ Yeah, it's fine.
Rinko
Are there any festival-like poses？ Can it be normal？
Rinko
Hmmm, so these outfits are what you call rare shots？
Rinko
"Give me some candy or I'll play a prank on you."？ How about something like this？
Rinko
Since we're here, take a cultural picture, okay？
Rinko
Let's take lots of pictures to remember our trip.
Rinko
Hehe. Christmas is a special day after all. Take cute pictures.
Rinko
The first photo of the year is Rinko▼
Rinko
It would be a nice keepsake if we could have a picture taken like this every year.
Rinko
I guess this is supposed to be a commemorative photo, too. Don't screw it up, okay？
Rinko
Hey. Are you sure you got the surrounding scenery in there？
Rinko
There are a lot of food stalls.
Anywhere you want to stop？
Well... then, that one！
Ah, ▲メニュー▲. Heh, that sounds delicious.
Yeah, it's delicious. Want some？
Well...
How do you like it？
Yeah, yummy！ Thanks for the food.
Rinko
There are a lot of food stalls.
Yeah.
Since we're here, do you want something to eat？
Lemme see...
▲メニュー１▲
▲メニュー２▲
▲メニュー３▲
▲メニュー４▲
▲メニュー５▲
After all, if you're going to eat at a food stall, you have to eat this.
Heh, sounds good.
Do you want some ▲小早川＊▲？
Delicious. Even more so when I have my boyfriend feed it to me. Hehe.
Rinko
I made a bento for you. Do you want some...？
Really！？ I wanna eat it！
You're too excited！ I'm your girlfriend, so we at least have to have lunch together.
Rinko
You know... I'm hungry. I made bento for you.
Did you make this？ Of course I'll eat it, ▲小早川＊▲！
Don't be in such a hurry, the bento won't run away.
Rinko
I worked hard and made bento for you. You'll eat it, right？
Of course！ It's handmade. I'm looking forward to it, ▲小早川＊▲.
If you're that happy with it... Hehe, I'm glad. Go ahead, eat up.
Rinko
Oh, what？
Rinko
It was your birthday. I really wanted to give it to you on that day.
Rinko
You see, it was our anniversary. That's why the present.
Rinko
A Christmas present. I couldn't give it to you on the day.
Rinko
I know it's a little past time, but here's your Valentine's Day present.
Thank you. Then I...
Rinko
I knew it. Hehe, thank you.
Thank you. I'm so happy.
Rinko
I'm glad you're happy with it. Take good care of it.
Rinko
Well, then, that's that. Next year, let's make sure we meet on the same day.
Right, sorry. Thanks for the present.
It's past White Day, but I got this as a return gift.
Rinko
Eh, really？
Sorry it took so long.
No, I don't mind. I'm glad you had it ready for me, thanks.
(I know it's past White Day, but maybe we can do something now...)
This is a late birthday present...
Rinko
It's long overdue, you know？
Sorry！ I didn't mean to forget.
I'm not mad at you. But we'll spend the next year together. Promise？
(Her birthday has passed, but I wonder if we can do something now, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Rinko
It was before we started dating, and I didn't think I had to give it to you... Well, just in case.
You don't have to worry so much about it, but I'm still very happy with it...
Yeah... I see. Hehe. Bye.
(Even though it was before we started dating, she gave me chocolate... I'll have to think about what to give her for White Day.)
Rinko
Oh, by the way, it's next week. Have you realized that？
Um...
The anniversary of when we started dating. You haven't forgotten, have you？
Of course not！
If that's the case, fine. But since we're here, let's do something memorable.
Something memorable, huh.
Because, you know, if we just have a normal date, it's no different than any other date.
Maybe buy matching items to commemorate the occasion！
What's that, it's too embarrassing. Rejected.
I see...
Let's think about it some more. It's fun to discuss things like this between the two of us, isn't it？
Yeah.
Rinko
For our anniversary, I think matching items are good.
Oh, I see. What would you like to do then？
Then, you know, I'd love to go to the mall with you tomorrow and we can decide together... What do you think？
Choosing a gift while talking to each other, huh... Yeah, I like that.
Right？ I'm sure it will be fun.
But why did you change your mind？ You rejected the idea.
Well, Rinko has her own feelings about that. When the day approaches, you feel like that, don't you？
What kind of feelings？
It's called... loverly feelings.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
ave you thought about where you want to go around from, ▲小早川＊▲？
Not yet... I think you're a little overzealous.
You think？
You don't have to be in such a hurry. You want to take your time when choosing a present.
...That's true, too. Let's take it slow.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yo, ▲小早川＊▲.
Too late... I was waiting for you.
I wasn't late, was I？
Even if you are not late, do not make your girlfriend wait for you.
...sorry.
Good. Let's take a look around, shall we？
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Hey, have you decided what you're going to get, ▲主人公＊▲？
Not yet. What about you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well... Oh, I'm not even going to waste my time thinking about this.
Well, let's get started with some shops.
Yeah. Let's go.
How about a key-chain...？
Rinko
Carved initials？ It's not a tourist attraction, you know, rejected.
Plate engraved with our names.
That's like a wedding gift.
I was kidding. What do you think we should buy ▲小早川＊▲？
I just thought I'd take a look into my boyfriend's sense of style. Just observation.
I told you it's a keepsake for the two of us, so we'll pick it out together.
I can't help it. Well, let's see from the other store over there, shall we？
Hehe, I got a good one.
I guess a girl's opinion is important. If it had been just me, I would never have been able to choose.
Rinko took the time to pick it out for you, so take good care of it. Okay？
If I'm going to buy something, I'd like to have it on hand.
Rinko
I guess so. But I don't want to make it look like a cuppa roux.
Why not？ I mean, it's a classic, right？
I don't like it because it's standard. We might look like an idiot couple.
Can't we buy matching ones？
It is acceptable if they are casually matching. It's a matter of taste.
That's a tough one...
It is the boyfriend's role to keep his head above water for his girlfriend. Do your best.
Yeah, this is good.
It took a long time, but I'm glad I chose a good one. Did you like it too, ▲小早川＊▲？
Not bad, right？ I have to give credit to my boyfriend for his efforts, too.
Flowers are the standard when it comes to gifts.
Rinko
I would be happy with any gift from my boyfriend.
Well, since we're here, let's both choose. Is there anything you want？
No... I don't think so.
I'll listen to whatever you want today, ▲小早川＊▲.
Not just things... I want to take my time today and look around... I want to hold your hand.
Take our time？
That's right. It's so sad to just pick a present and be done with it. Right？
Hehe. It was a lot of fun▼
it's hard to decide on a gift, isn't it, ▲小早川＊▲？
It's all right, I bought it. It's called "the result is all right".
(When I was choosing, you looked like you were having a good time, ▲小早川＊▲...)
I hope we can celebrate our anniversary together like this again next year.
Rinko
Next year？ ...if you don't change your mind.
Rinko's feelings will never change, though.
Hmm？ What did you say？
I didn't say anything. You misheard. Maybe your it was your imagination... Oh, we part ways here.
You know... thanks. I had a good time today.
...yeah.
Okay, that's the end.
I guess it's time to say goodbye, huh.
Don't look like you're saying goodbye for life. You can see me anytime. You'll see me tomorrow... and forever after.
Maybe you don't like the present, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
It is not like that. I want you to say it with words, you know？
You wouldn't just give me a gift and think that's all there is to it, would you？
No, I would not.
Well, then, don't you have something to say on special occasions？
I see... I'm really happy you're my girlfriend, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko, too. So... why don't we do it？ Before someone else comes along.
What！？ ...yeah.
Thanks for today. It was a day to remember.
For me too. I hope we can celebrate like this again next year.
Yeah. Okay, see you later.
Rinko
The guy at the shop asked me if you and Rinko were a couple.
That was a little embarrassing.
There's nothing to be ashamed of. He's not wrong.
Huh？ I thought you would be more embarrassed, ▲小早川＊▲.
That's not true... And we arrived to our destination.
You know, you and Rinko are lovers, right？ The how about a... goodbye kiss.
What！？ ...yeah.
If you don't hurry up, someone will come.
Geez... are we done？
For today. I love you, and I always will, so we can do it anytime, ▲小早川＊▲.
Geez... you're an idiot. You don't have to say that...
Haha. See you later.
Rinko
Your birthday is coming up soon, right？
Come to think of it, yes.
...maybe you don't even remember your own birthday？
I remember, but I'm not really aware of it.
Birthday is a special day. If you're like that, it'll go by just like any other day, you know？
That's what they say. Are you going to celebrate it, ▲小早川＊▲？
You want me to celebrate？
That's, well, I'd be happy to have my girlfriend celebrate it with me.
I have no choice. I'll think of something.
Just joking. I've had "boyfriend's birthday" marked in my schedule book for a long time.
Rinko
Keep your schedule open tomorrow night.
Tomorrow night...？
It's your birthday, right？ Perhaps... you've made some plans？
Not yet. Will you celebrate it with me, ▲小早川＊▲？
I told you I'd think about it. So, wait for me at your place.
My place？ I thought it was an invitation to go somewhere.
We can do that any time we want. There's only one birthday a year, remember？
That's true, but... what will you do？
That's for the day. Rinko will make your birthday unforgettable.
(An unforgettable birthday. I'm looking forward to it.)
What's in that shopping bag ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
It's your birthday, isn't it？
Don't tell me... are you going to cook for me, ▲小早川＊▲？
What's with the surprise？ I see. You don't want to eat it. Then should I stop cooking？
I was just surprised because it was so sudden. Of course I want some！
Okay, I'll borrow your kitchen.
(I wonder what in the world she's going to cook.)
Here, Rinko's homemade food... Ah, geez, don't be so rash.
You made it for me, so I wanted to eat right away, ▲小早川＊▲.
Don't panic, they won't run away from you, so savor your food.
I've been waiting for you. Huh？ A shopping bag, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
It must be lonely to have a ready-made meal on your birthday, isn't it？
...so you mean, you'll cook ▲小早川＊▲？
That's right. Can I borrow your kitchen...？
Yeah. You can use it however you like.
...What？ It's hard to do it if you're staring at me like that.
I see, yeah！ Well, I'll look forward to seeing it when it's ready.
Here it is, Rinko's special homemade food.
Amazing, isn't something elaborate today？
It's... well, it's your birthday. I can't vouch for the taste, but... how do you like it？
Welcome. What's wrong, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Hehe. Sorry to keep you waiting. I was shopping and it got late.
Shopping, you say...
I told you I'd make your birthday unforgettable. That's why Rinko is cooking for you tonight▼
Really？ That makes me happy.
I'll put my best effort into making it. Look forward to it.
(I'm looking forward to today's food made by you, ▲小早川＊▲.)
Ta-da.
Oh, amazing. Did you make all these dishes, ▲小早川＊▲？
Yup. I followed the recipe exactly, but... I hope it's palatable. Hey, can you try it now？
It was really delicious. I think you have improved your cooking skills, haven't you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
I see. I'm glad you liked it.
And that thing behind... could that be a present for me？
Yes. I wonder why you found it before I gave it to you... Here, for you.
Because you don't give me things very often.
Even Rinko was thinking about timing and stuff. It's okay, though, because I'm going to give it to you anyway.
A home-cooked meal and a present from my girlfriend on my birthday, I'm a lucky guy, aren't I？
You're exaggerating. If you are so happy, it sounds fake.
I'm not lying, I' m really happy. Thank you, ▲小早川＊▲.
...yeah.
You said you couldn't guarantee the taste, but it was delicious.
Rinko
I see. I'm glad... You can have this too.
A present？ Are you sure？
It's your birthday, of course it's good.
You made me a home-cooked meal and gave me a present. I'm very happy.
You don't have to be that happy.
Of course, anyone would be pleased to have his girlfriend do this much for him.
I see... Then maybe it was worth the effort.
Yeah, it was the best birthday ever. Thanks.
That's because, you know, I'm your girlfriend... so it's natural.
The food was delicious.
Rinko
I'm really glad... I was actually worried what if it didn't turn out well.
And, you know...
Yes, this. Your birthday present.
You made me a home-cooked meal, and you even gave me a present？
Wouldn't it be weird if it was your birthday and you didn't get a present？
I was incredibly happy just to have a home-cooked meal.
I hope you like it...
You chose it, didn't you？ Then how could I not like it, ▲小早川＊▲？
Really？ Well then, take good care of it, okay？
Rinko
Well, I guess it's time to go home.
Sorry to keep you up this late. I'll take you home.
Yeah... but I think better not. I can go home alone.
...Well, then, have a safe trip home.
Yeah... that's it？
That's it, you ask...
You know... won't you do it？ Your girlfriend's about to leave, you know？
...Okay, I'm going home.
Thanks for today. It was a great birthday.
...I'm glad you're happy. See ya.
Rinko
Oh... I have to go home soon.
It's that time already？
I know you don't want me to leave, but I can't just not go home, can I？
That's true...
It's hard to have a lonely boyfriend, really.
Lonely, huh... well, yeah I'll miss you.
Such a loner, why don't you do it like you always do？ Come on... give me a hug...
How's that？ Now you won't be lonely, will you？
Yup. Now that might be the best birthday present I've ever had.
What does that mean... Well, I hope you're happy. See you later.
Rinko
Is it that late already？
Look, if you don't go home soon, your parents will worry.
Don't act like you are too old.
Hey, before I leave, a question... How was your birthday？
I was happy that you celebrated with me, ▲小早川＊▲.
I'm glad you're happy. Well then... now it's time for Rinko's request, okay？
Request？ What is it?
A reward... right？ Shall we kiss...？
Hehe. Thanks▼
...Well, then, have a safe trip home.
Yes. See you later.
Rinko
Hey, you didn't forget... did you？ It's about time.
What do you mean？
You really don't remember？ I can't believe you forgot your girlfriend's birthday.
I'm just kidding. How could I forget your birthday, ▲小早川＊▲.
Sorry, I guess I pressured you. But you don't need to do anything special.
What about a party or something？
I had a party thrown for me every year when I was little...
Let's do it then.
I don't need that kind of exaggeration. Rinko would rather spend time with you than do anything special.
(Are you sure that's what you want to do...？)
For example, isn't there a place you'd like to visit on your birthday, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Not especially if you suddenly say that.
Even though it's your birthday？
Well, let's go to karaoke, shall we？
That's the same as always.
No problem. Oh yeah, let's go to the arcade and play some fighting games, okay？ And then we'll finish it off with a live show.
How about a full course of Rinko's favorite foods？ It's not easy to visit all of them.
Is that what you want？
It's enough. You don't get to experience a day full of your favorite things very often.
(If you want to go, I guess that's fine, ▲小早川＊▲.)
Rinko
Sorry to keep you waiting, ▲主人公＊▲.
Happy birthday, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hehe, thanks. So, shall we start with karaoke？
I want to ask. Are you sure today's date should be the same as usual？
I said it's fine. And it's not the same, okay？
That's, well, the schedule is like an endurance race, starting with karaoke and ending with live music.
That's what I mean. We're wasting time, so let's get going.
You could have told me more about the places I wouldn't normally go.
It's okay. I just came in and wanted to be one of the first to play a new gaming game.
It doesn't have to be your birthday does it, does it？
Perhaps you're not happy？
Hmmm, well, if it makes you happy, so be it, ▲小早川＊▲.
That's what I mean. I'll give you plenty of hugs today.
Just because it's your birthday, I'd ask you to go easy on me there.
Hehe. What should I do？
Rinko
Mmm, you sang！
Don't skip... you okay after this？
It's okay. Let's go to the arcade then！
Come on, hurry！
I get it.
If you don't hurry, the concert will start.
A-All right...
Ah, that was good. Best performance I've ever seen.
That's good to know...
Hmm, what's up？
After singing so much at karaoke, and then shouting at a live concert, right？ Your voice is already rattling.
You're so sloppy.
You don't seem to be tired at all. Didn't you jump all the way through the concert ▲小早川＊▲？
It's a pleasant tiredness. Rinko is just fine with karaoke again after this.
(Give me a break on that... It's been a flurry of activity all day...)
Rinko
...It's kinda nice to have your birthday celebrated.
But can't they celebrate it at you house too, ▲小早川＊▲？
That's other thing. But a birthday spent with your boyfriend is special.
Is that how it is？
That's just the way it is. So... thanks. I had a great time today.
...haha.
Did Rinko say something funny？
Haha... The way you say it with a frown on your face, ▲小早川＊▲...
Oh, you laughed again！ I'm going to get angry, okay？
Sorry, I won't laugh again！
Rinko
Hey. How was our date today？
...Yeah, it was fun.
You don't have to force yourself, you know？
I'm not forcing myself, but I'm also tired.
But was it really fun？
Yes, you betcha！
Then that's okay. I just wondered if Rinko was the only one having fun.
It was fun to see you enjoying yourself. Even now ▲小早川＊▲.
...You'd be embarrassed if they stared at you that much.
Haha. You don't have to be so shy.
Rinko
Sorry about today.
What！？ Why？
I just thought maybe I was being unreasonable and dragging you around.
That's not true. It's your birthday, so as long as you're happy, that's all that matters, ▲小早川＊▲.
But you're tired indeed, aren't you？
Well... a little bit. But it was more fun than that, really.
That's fine then...
Hmm？
Do you want to go to the karaoke again？
Rejected！
Tsk！
I know, I have a birthday present I want to give you.
Rinko
To Rinko...？
Who else is there？
...Yeah, thanks.
I know, I have a birthday present I want to give you.
Rinko
You didn't have to me. I'm just glad that you went out with me today.
It's okay, these are my feelings.
...I see. Thanks.
I know, I have a birthday present I want to give you.
Rinko
To Rinko？ What is it？
I hope you like it.
Hehe. Thank you. You don't mind if I take a look inside, do you？
Rinko
Nice！ Rinko loves this sense of style.
Rinko
You know exactly what Rinko likes, hehe！ Thanks.
Rinko
Rinko wanted something like this. I'm glad you figured it out. Thanks.
Rinko
This kind of thing is good, isn't it？ Thanks.
Rinko
Is this what you think of Rinko？ I see, maybe it's a new discovery.
Rinko
You thought hard about it. Thanks.
Rinko
What！？ ...You know, this... I guess I have no choice.
Rinko
I thought you knew a little more about Rinko's tastes...
Rinko
I know you worked hard to choose the right one for me... Yeah, I'll just take your feelings.
Rinko
Hey. Are you going to follow me into my house？ I'm fine right here.
I see. See you later.
Yeah, see ya.
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲？
You know what, I have a few more minutes. And...
That's it for today. You know... will you celebrate Rinko's birthday again next year？
You don't have to ask that, do you？
I see... I'll see you next time.
Rinko
I'm fine right here.
I see... huh, what？
You know... when you say goodbye, isn't there something you're supposed to do？
What！？
You could have led more.
...yeah. Well, good night.
Good night. And hey... had a great time today. Thanks.
Today you're very honest, ▲小早川＊▲.
You think？ Hey, I hope next year's birthday is as fun as this one.
I'll think about it now. See you, good night.
Rinko
Well, then, here we are. Goodbye, I guess...
You don't have to say it like it's a lifelong separation.
Because as much fun as I had today, I will be sad when I have to say goodbye.
I hope this is such a fun day next year and all the birthdays after that...
I'm sure it will.
Yeah, I'm sure it will. You know... can I just... for a minute？
Hehe. That's a relief. Maybe I can have a good dream today.
See you.
Yeah, good night.
Rinko
I saw bamboo branches decorated in town. Tanabata, huh...
Yeah. By the way, it's already next week.
Yeah. What kind of wishes do you have？
My wishes... what about you ▲小早川＊▲？
For Rinko it's a secret.
Then, mine are also a secret.
Ah, it's not fair... I know. Let's bring bamboo strips with our wishes on the day of the event. That would be good, right？
In that case... yeah, though it's a little embarrassing.
No. We'll show each other. Okay？ That's a promise.
Yeah, I get it.
Did you bring the bamboo strips with you？
Rinko
Just in case.
Where are your wishes, ▲小早川＊▲...
Oh, geez, don't look at it. Hey, where's your bamboo strip？
This is mine.
Rinko
▲小早川＊▲？
How often do you do this... What if other people see it？
They can' t see it, so it doesn't matter, does it？
Idiot... Hehe.
Here, this is mine.
Rinko
...Is this your wish？
Yup... Was that something bad？
It's Tanabata. Orihime and Hikoboshi. Think about the situation a little more.
(Did I put you in a bad mood somehow...？)
Actually... I forgot to prepare my bamboo strips.
Rinko
What！？ For real？ ...I can't believe it. You promised me.
Sorry！
Being sorry doesn't cut it. Come one, write it here, right now.
...yes.
Rinko
Look, look. That area is the Milky Way.
So that's Hikoboshi and... that one is Orihime.
I'm glad it cleared up. Two people who love each other can see each other again.
We are lucky to be able to see each other whenever we want to.
Can I go by your side？
...yeah. What's up？
I wanted to be closer to the one I love. I don't want to be separated from them.
And one more request, would you mind？
It's Tanabata, so it's fine. What kind of request？
You know what, let's... kiss...？
Hehe. Did Hikoboshi and Orihime see us？
They are already preparing for the festival at Towano Shrine, but I guess it's that time of year already.
Rinko
It's already next month.
Shall we go together？
No, Rinko will go with her friends.
Why not？ Why don't we go together？
Because, you know, there is a legend about the Towano Festival.
Legend？ I think it was something about the god of love at the shrine...
Yes. If two people who are already a couple visit the shrine during the festival, the gods will get jealous and separate them.
Maybe it's just a saying. But you know, just in case.
(I think you're too worried about this...)
Rinko
Today is the Towano Festival. I heard it's already bustling with people since this morning.
Speaking of which, are you going with friends, ▲小早川＊▲？
I don't know, I just can't get a hold on everyone...
Go with me then.
...So what if the legend is true？
Do you know any couple who broke up because of that, ▲小早川＊▲？
Hmmm... I don't know any.
See？ Do you think our love can be defeated by such legend？
Isn't it embarrassing to say love...？ ...I don't have a choice. If you want to go that far, Rinko will go with you.
Then it's settled. Right？
Rinko
Sorry to keep you waiting.
What？ You're staring too much... is it weird？
Nah. You look great in yukata, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hehe. Thanks.
Yeah. Let's go over there. They have goldfish scooping.
Oh, hey. Running too fast is dangerous.
Hey, hey. Are you good at scooping goldfish？
Who knows. Maybe I'm better at this than, ▲小早川＊▲.
Whatever you say. I'm not going to go easy on you.
Rinko
It's almost the end of the Towano Festival.
That went by so fast.
Then... the last day is a fireworks display.
